Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.19,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs50\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\bord1\pos(351,405)}Prvi Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Svi brodovi, napad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.08,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\bord1\pos(280,85)}Vežba
